---
import "../styles/globals.css";
---

<div class="h-full overflow-x-hidden">
  <section
    id="community-conduct"
    class="relative z-20 py-12 md:py-20 border-t border-white/10 overflow-hidden"
  >
    <div
      class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto md:grid md:grid-cols-10 md:grid-rows-5 gap-0 relative z-10 md:min-h-[600px]"
    >
      <!-- Horizontal Lines (Grid Row 3) - Visible on Left, Hidden on Right -->
      <div
        class="hidden md:block col-start-1 col-end-11 row-start-3 row-end-4 border-t-2 border-b-2 border-dashed border-[#999999]/50 pointer-events-none z-20"
        style="mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, black 50%, transparent 50%); -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, black 50%, transparent 50%);"
      >
      </div>

      <!-- Left: Title and Intro -->
      <!-- Title: Rows 1-2 -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col h-full md:col-start-1 md:col-end-6 md:row-start-1 md:row-end-3 md:border-r-2 md:border-dashed md:border-[#999999]/50"
      >
        <div class="p-6 md:p-10 flex items-start h-full">
          <h1
            class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-[5rem] leading-[0.9] font-bold text-[#FFFDD0] uppercase tracking-tighter break-words"
          >
            CSI-VIT<br />
            <span class="text-[#FF5F4A]">CODE OF CONDUCT</span>
          </h1>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Subtitle: Row 3 -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col h-full md:col-start-1 md:col-end-6 md:row-start-3 md:row-end-4 md:border-r-2 md:border-dashed md:border-[#999999]/50"
      >
        <div class="px-6 md:px-10 py-4 md:py-0 flex items-center h-full">
          <div
            class="text-[#FF5F4A] text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold font-['Inter'] leading-tight"
          >
            Core Values & Expectations
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Intro Text: Rows 4-5 -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col h-full md:col-start-1 md:col-end-6 md:row-start-4 md:row-end-6 md:border-r-2 md:border-dashed md:border-[#999999]/50"
      >
        <div class="p-6 md:p-10 h-full flex items-end">
          <div
            class="text-left text-gray-300 text-xs sm:text-sm font-mono leading-relaxed max-w-lg"
          >
            AS THE VIT UNIVERSITY CSI STUDENT CHAPTER, OUR VALUES AND
            EXPECTATIONS ARE GROUNDED IN THE CSI Code of Ethics AND PROFESSIONAL
            CONDUCT. COMPUTING PROFESSIONALS HAVE A PROFOUND IMPACT ON SOCIETY
            AND MUST PRIORITISE THE PUBLIC GOOD.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Detailed Points (Spans Full Height on Desktop) -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col h-full md:col-start-6 md:col-end-11 md:row-start-1 md:row-end-6"
      >
        <!-- Scrollable content area for detailed points -->
        <div class="p-6 md:p-10 h-full overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar">
          <div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 text-gray-300 font-mono text-xs sm:text-sm leading-relaxed"
          >
            <!-- 1. General Ethical Principles -->
            <div>
              <h3
                class="text-[#FF5F4A] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 text-base"
              >
                1. General Ethical Principles
              </h3>
              <p class="mb-2">Computing professionals should:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2 text-gray-400">
                <li>Contribute to the well-being of society and avoid harm.</li>
                <li>
                  Be honest, trustworthy, fair, and respectful toward all
                  individuals.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Uphold inclusivity, accessibility, and non-discrimination.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Respect intellectual property, protect users’ privacy, and
                  honour confidentiality.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Consider the broader implications of their work on society and
                  environment.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- 2. Professional Responsibilities -->
            <div>
              <h3
                class="text-[#FF5F4A] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 text-base"
              >
                2. Professional Responsibilities
              </h3>
              <p class="mb-2">Professionals are expected to:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2 text-gray-400">
                <li>Deliver high-quality work and valid expertise.</li>
                <li>Follow laws, policies, and professional standards.</li>
                <li>
                  Evaluate systems for risks and design secure, reliable
                  solutions.
                </li>
                <li>Access systems only with proper authorisation.</li>
                <li>Promote public understanding and engage in peer review.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- 3. Leadership Responsibilities -->
            <div>
              <h3
                class="text-[#FF5F4A] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 text-base"
              >
                3. Leadership Responsibilities
              </h3>
              <p class="mb-2">Leaders must:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2 text-gray-400">
                <li>Ensure goals prioritise the public good.</li>
                <li>Foster ethical behaviour, transparency, and respect.</li>
                <li>Support team well-being and growth.</li>
                <li>Enforce sound governance and policies.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- 4. Compliance -->
            <div>
              <h3
                class="text-[#FF5F4A] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 text-base"
              >
                4. Compliance With Code
              </h3>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2 text-gray-400">
                <li>Uphold and promote the CSI Code.</li>
                <li>Address ethical concerns responsibly.</li>
                <li>
                  Unethical behaviour is incompatible with CSI membership.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<style>
  /* Custom Scrollbar for the text area */
  .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {
    width: 6px;
  }
  .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }
  .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: #ff5f4a;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
  .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
    background: #ff3f2a;
  }
</style>
